contour plot¶

In [8]:
x <- seq(-pi, pi, length = 50)
y <- x
f <- outer(x, y, function(x, y) cos(y) / (1 + x^2))
contour(x, y, f, nlevels = 10)
In [9]:
df = melt(f)   # wide to long format
ggplot(df, aes(Var1, Var2, z = value)) +
  geom_contour(bins = 10, color = 'black') +
  geom_text_contour(aes(z = value)) +
  xlab('X') + ylab('Y') +
  ggtitle('Contour Plot f(x,y)') + 
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))   # hjust = 0 (left) 1(right)
